  "body": "- [V] I've asked for help in the [Truffle Gitter](http://gitter.im/Consensys/truffle) before filing this issue.\r\n\r\n---------------------------\r\n\r\n## Issue\r\n\r\nI have a basic setup of truffle and Quorum network running on localhost.\r\nWhen I try to migrate the contract compiled with 0.5.8 (default compiler for truffle@5.0.24) the console emits error.\r\nSo, I tried changed the compiler version to 0.5.0 in truffle-config.js, it migrates with no issue.\r\n\r\n## Steps to Reproduce\r\n\r\n* Network:\r\nQuorum-maker, 1 node setup, unlocked.\r\n./setup.sh and then everything as default\r\n\r\nHere's my truffle-config.js\r\n\r\n```\r\nmodule.exports = {\r\n  networks: {\r\n    development: {\r\n      host: \"127.0.0.1\",\r\n      port: 22000,\r\n      network_id: \"*\",\r\n      type: \"quorum\",\r\n      gas: 450000000,\r\n      gasPrice:0\r\n    },\r\n  compilers: {\r\n    solc: {\r\n      version: \"0.5.8\"\r\n    }\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nWhen I change the compiler version from \"0.5.8\" to \"0.5.0\" then everything works just fine.\r\n\r\n## Expected Behavior\r\n\r\nSmooth migration & deploy\r\n\r\n## Actual Results\r\n\r\n```\r\n~/test 6s\r\nâ¯ truffle deploy --reset --network development\r\n\r\nCompiling your contracts...\r\n===========================\r\n> Everything is up to date, there is nothing to compile.\r\n\r\nRunning migration: 1_initial_migration.js\r\nDeploying Migrations...\r\nMigrations: 0x641fbb055666a2564Eb85Eaa75Cc8FFC225E1003\r\nSaving successful migration to network...\r\nError encountered, bailing. Network state unknown. Review successful transactions manually.\r\nError: Error: StatusError: Transaction: 0x33d98e9ad98f1515b239d18ad5db6417a7a0cac0100c8ac6e9fa777c101180e3 exited with an error (status 0) after consuming all gas.\r\n     Please check that the transaction:\r\n     - satisfies all conditions set by Solidity `assert` statements.\r\n     - has enough gas to execute the full transaction.\r\n     - does not trigger an invalid opcode by other means (ex: accessing an array out of bounds).\r\n    at Object.run (/Users/ace/.nvm/versions/node/v10.15.3/lib/node_modules/truffle/build/webpack:/packages/truffle-migrate/index.js:92:1)\r\n    at process._tickCallback (internal/process/next_tick.js:68:7)\r\nTruffle v5.0.24 (core: 5.0.24)\r\nNode v10.15.3\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Environment\r\n\r\n* Operating System: MacOS 10.14.5\r\n* Ethereum client: Quorum maker v2.6.2 Built on Quorum 2.2.1\r\n* Truffle version (`truffle version`): Truffle v5.0.24 (core: 5.0.24)\r\n* node version (`node --version`): Node v10.15.3\r\n* npm version (`npm --version`): 6.4.1\r\n",
