    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "I believe the workaround here is to set the `evmVersion` in your solc settings:\r\n\r\n```\r\ncompilers: {\r\n  solc: {\r\n    settings: {\r\n      evmVersion: \"byzantium\"\r\n    }\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nWe've been trying to figure out a way to make this default on Quorum networks, but it's tricky because of the disconnect between compile/migrate.",
